snippet.title: 🎮 TankWars.io Gameplay 1.0 – PlayOn .io
snippet.description:
TankWars .IO NO DOWNLOAD! JUST PURE AWESOMENESS!
► Play TankWars.io: http://TankWars.io/
Free browser game – hours of entertainment!
Created by PlayOn .IO

📌 Join us!
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tankwarsio/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayOn_io
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/tankwars/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playon.io/
G+: https://plus.google.com/u/0/+TankwarsIo
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/TankWarsio

Welcome to the fight Commander 🎖️

Welcome to http://TankWars.io one of the the most exhilarating and addictive browser game in the world of IO games / MMO games. Take command of your tank and annihilate the enemy before he annihilates you! Be prepared to battle players from all over the world. Use your power ups to your advantage. Be aware of the planes! Some might get you! Others will help you with drops!

💑 Have a blast with Your Friends
– Make a party!
– Join your friends!
– Make new ones!

👍 Customize Your Tank
– See amazing community skins!
– Make your own awesome tankwars.io skin!
– All in the TankWars 🎮 unique customization editor!

👑 Lots of future Game Modes planned
– ⚔️ Conquest
– 👑 KingDM (King DeathMatch)
– More modes coming soon!

🎨 Make Your own Maps
--In the near future, it will be possible to contribute to the game by making new maps. Other players will be able to vote your masterpiece into the game. Post/contact us to join the beta test team!

💬 Contribute to the community
– Our vision is to make the best .io game in the world. We can’t do that without listening! Share your thoughts with us so we together can achieve that goal.

▼ TankWars.io Videos
🎨 New Maps Sketches https://youtu.be/0T3ax3XWn0g
⚡ Scout Tank gameplay https://youtu.be/j-ZG9TVkko0
💪 Mammoth Tank gameplay https://youtu.be/4u9AbxcAW9Y
👊 Tank STOMP Power-up https://youtu.be/dOw47w3CmGQ
🎮 Tank Teleport Power-up https://youtu.be/hNIoxU83SaI

Song: Silencyde - Shroud
Silencyde Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/silencyde
Silencyde Facebook: https://facebook.com/Silencyde
Silentcyde YouTube: https://youtube.com/user/Silencyde
Silentcyde WWW: http://www.silencyde.com/
